@juliastonemusic has created a record of Australian songs covered by artists from around the world… @thenational @damienrice @paulkellyofficial @martha.wainwright @joanaspolicewoman @kurtvile @petitbiscuit @pommeofficial @Dansultanmusic @dopelemonmusic and @dermotkennedy have all contributed a track for this record. 
The money raised will go towards supporting us and some other amazing organisations working towards creating a better future for Australia and rebuilding during and after this bushfire crisis. 
You can pre-order the record at songsforaustralia.com

#Repost @chrishemsworth
・・・
Hi everyone. Like you, I want to support the fight against the bushfires here in Australia. My family and I are contributing a million dollars. Hopefully you guys can chip in too. Every penny counts so whatever you can muster up is greatly appreciated. In my bio I’ve added links to support the fire fighters, organisations and charities who are working flat out to provide support and relief during this devastating and challenging time. Beyond appreciative to everyone around the world for their well wishes and donations. It really does make a difference, so dig deep!  Love ya.

Excited to announce a movie I worked on called Killerman will be released in the USA on August 30th. I’m incredibly proud of the work everyone did on it. It was an absolute honor to work with my friend Emory Cohen again, one of my favorite actors, Malik Bader, an extremely creative and intelligent director, and the brilliant Ken Seng for his work as Director of Photography. Blood, sweat and tears were shed from all who were involved. Independent film making is always a tough thing to pull off and I just want to thank all the hard-working people who helped make it happen. @killermanofficial

Hi all 
Just a quick note to say that Miley and I have recently separated and I wish her nothing but health and happiness going forward. 
This is a private matter and I have not made, nor will I be making, any comments to any journalists or media outlets.  Any reported quotes attributed to me are false. 
Peace and Love.
